OL,3,G```````R(,/E"Y" IS FOR...G`````````````
OL,4,EYAHOO!BThe most popular Internet search
OL,5,Bengine, and thoroughly useful unless   
OL,6,Byou're looking for anything even       
OL,7,Bslightly morally questionable.         
OL,9,EYOBBOBWhat old people traditionally    
OL,10,Bcall the idiots who wear puffy jackets 
OL,11,Band hang around in menacing gangs in   
OL,12,Bvideo game arcades and McDonalds. These
OL,13,Bpeople are never, ever, seen in public 
OL,14,Bhouses, for some reason.               
OL,16,BPerhaps they fear an assault from a    
OL,17,Bdrunken thug, who has realised, in some
OL,18,Bmoment of lucidity, that puffy jackets 
OL,19,Bdo not deserve to live.                
