OL,3,G```````R(,/E"Y" IS FOR...G`````````````
OL,5,EYOUTH TVBConsidering that games are an 
OL,6,Bessential part of this country's youth 
OL,7,Bculture, it's astonishing how badly    
OL,8,Bwrong producers get their coverage of  
OL,9,Bcomputer and video games.              
OL,11,BWe refuse to believe that any "youth"  
OL,12,Bin this country respects the opinion of
OL,13,Ba "Ben the Boffin" or that bad-haired, 
OL,14,B"computer boy" from Live and Kicking.  
OL,16,BPubescent gamesplayers want someone to 
OL,17,Blook up to. They don't want to be      
OL,18,Bhanded advice by someone they'd        
OL,19,Bordinarily beat up.                    
