OL,5,EZBHad the misfortune to be developed   
OL,6,Balongside Command and Conquer, but was 
OL,7,Breleased some considerable time later. 
OL,8,BIts closely-related gameplay resulted  
OL,9,Bin the game being labelled a C&C clone,
OL,10,Bwhich wasn't fair; Z wasn't anywhere   
OL,11,Bnearly as good.                        
OL,13,EZED TWOBSome sort of UK development    
OL,14,Bhouse that used to have a link to      
OL,15,BDigitiser on its Web site. It isn't    
OL,16,Bthere anymore, and they also ignored us
OL,17,Bwhen we asked them to fill out a "Space
OL,18,BGents" questionaire. Therefore, we     
OL,19,Bsuspect their games are rubbish.       
